    Connect with Google Drive
    You need to authenticate with Google Drive to be able to keep your screens in real-time sync. We only extract images and never modify or delete files.

    We couldn't connect to Dropbox

    Marvel failed to connect to Dropbox. This could be because Dropbox is blocked on your network or if you're using a proxy that doesn't allow us to connect.

    If you can, disable any proxies or contact your network administrator.

    Do you have multiple Dropbox accounts?

    It looks like youve used your browser to log into another Dropbox account which is causing a clash with Marvel. Log out, and log back in with the correct account!

    Log out
